WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.080
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.080 --> 00:00:02.520
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:02.780 --> 00:00:06.699
I have some things on my heart, but first off, let's give God some praise.

00:00:06.699 --> 00:00:11.657
For the Lord is good and his mercy endures forever.

00:00:23.520 --> 00:00:29.474
Father, I thank you that you endure forever and your mercy is new every morning.

00:00:29.474 --> 00:00:31.920
Great is your faithfulness to me, oh God.

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:34.429
Thank you, Father, for all that you're going to do today.

00:00:34.676 --> 00:00:39.806
I ask you, Father, to anoint this broadcast, this video today, and this YouTube video.

00:00:42.020 --> 00:00:46.360
I thank you, Father, that you speak through my vocal cords and you think through my mind.

00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:50.239
None of me and all of you, in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:00:50.239 --> 00:00:51.520
I thank you, Father.

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:59.359
I have an urgency in my heart for what's coming and to tell the people that Jesus is coming.

00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:05.857
Well, this is what I have for y'all today.

00:01:05.857 --> 00:01:10.009
I was driving down the road and the Lord just decided to speak.

00:01:10.009 --> 00:01:13.680
I mean, the prophetic unction just hit me hard.

00:01:14.448 --> 00:01:22.600
Like I said, I do not consider myself a prophet, but when I pray, I see visions and the Lord shows me things to come.

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:35.058
He showed me Israel, and I saw a major event about to take place in Israel.

00:01:35.058 --> 00:01:43.400
I saw at this time people in the streets with prayer shawls like what I have.

00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:56.099
They had these prayer things, they had the Israeli flag, and they had it over their shoulders, kind of like what they do at a sporting event, but they had it like this and it was draped around them.

00:01:57.200 --> 00:02:02.227
They were celebrating in the streets, saying, "The deliverer has come.

00:02:02.227 --> 00:02:03.669
The deliverer has come.

00:02:05.310 --> 00:02:14.088
" The women were dancing in the streets and the men were dancing, and they were celebrating some kind of victory.

00:02:14.088 --> 00:02:19.840
I do not know what this was, if it was war or whatever.

00:02:20.587 --> 00:02:26.640
All I know is they were celebrating something that had happened in the streets in Israel.

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:28.560
I saw rabbis.

00:02:28.560 --> 00:02:43.931
I saw Orthodox Jews with their hats on with curls and long beards, and they were weeping at this sight, at this experience.

00:02:44.262 --> 00:02:46.491
They were rocking at the Wailing Wall.

00:02:46.491 --> 00:02:52.444
I could see them praying and weeping at the Wailing Wall, and I could see them throughout the streets.

00:02:53.582 --> 00:02:58.560
I saw them actually say, "We've been in error.

00:02:58.560 --> 00:03:01.040
We have been in error in some of our teachings.

00:03:07.634 --> 00:03:19.199
" The Holy Spirit had gotten a hold of them and they were telling the people—I saw them teaching and telling the people that they had been in error about some things and they were going back and correcting things that they had been teaching that were in error.

00:03:19.199 --> 00:03:23.840
I saw a glory explosion over the Jewish people.

00:03:24.380 --> 00:03:32.939
A mighty revival started to break out in the streets in Jerusalem and all of the other areas of Israel.

00:03:32.939 --> 00:03:41.573
They were breaking forth in a revival of healings and demonstrations and manifestations of the glory.

00:03:41.573 --> 00:03:54.610
And the Lord said, "I'm going to become real to this generation like I had been in the past with the children of Israel when they were delivered out of the hand of Egypt.

00:03:54.610 --> 00:04:11.813
I'm going to do another wave of my presence, of my glory, over this generation, and they will see that I am real and that I am their Messiah, that I am God to them.

00:04:12.147 --> 00:04:22.1000
" The Lord showed me a great and mighty wave of his presence over all of the people.

00:04:22.1000 --> 00:04:25.759
But they were delivered from something.

00:04:25.943 --> 00:04:30.052
Like I said, I do not know what this was about, but they were dancing in the streets.

00:04:30.346 --> 00:04:34.320
I could see the rabbis and the tears that were flowing.

00:04:37.337 --> 00:04:47.919
There was a heavy-set man, and I don't know who this man was, but he had chubbier, heavier cheeks and a longer, silvery-peppered beard.

00:04:47.919 --> 00:04:50.053
I could see gray in his beard.

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:54.329
He was a rabbi, and he had glasses on and he was rocking.

00:04:54.631 --> 00:05:03.829
I remember seeing these curls, but I could see the people and they were teaching that "we were erring in our ways," and they knew that they were corrected about some things.

00:05:03.977 --> 00:05:06.639
I just thought it was amazing in this visitation.

00:05:06.888 --> 00:05:17.424
The Lord just told me that he was going to become real, and I don't want to keep rehashing that, but I'm just going back over my mind, remembering everything I was shown.

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:21.620
Then the Lord showed me this.

00:05:21.620 --> 00:05:32.160
He said, "Brandon, I'm going to uncap the wells of revival in America.

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:42.709
" And he said to me, "The great healing revivals that took place in the 1930s and 40s—you know, the tent revivals back whenever A.

00:05:42.709 --> 00:05:43.303
A.

00:05:43.303 --> 00:05:54.000
Allen, Jack Coe, William Branham, Smith, not Kenneth Hagin, but you know, John G.

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:56.000
Lake, that era of ministers.

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:59.199
" He told me Aimee Semple McPherson, and it goes on and on.

00:06:00.489 --> 00:06:02.999
He said, "Those wells were capped.

00:06:02.999 --> 00:06:05.400
" People have wondered, "Where has that gone?

00:06:05.400 --> 00:06:06.299
" They were capped.

00:06:06.299 --> 00:06:09.579
I looked up what the word 'capped' means.

00:06:09.919 --> 00:06:11.967
What does it mean to cap a well?

00:06:12.223 --> 00:06:28.544
The wells that are no longer being used but might be needed in the future can be sealed with a cap that covers the top of the well casing pipe to prevent unauthorized access and contamination.

00:06:30.331 --> 00:06:39.291
A cap is a temporary groundwater protection solution that allows a well to be used at a later time.

00:06:39.291 --> 00:06:55.084
He brought up the scripture in Genesis and he was talking about Isaac bringing forth the old wells that Abraham had dug, that the Philistines put dirt on and filled up, and capped those wells off.

00:06:59.509 --> 00:07:09.280
But the Lord was showing me that he's uncapping those wells of revival.

00:07:09.280 --> 00:07:11.063
He's uncapping all those deep wells.

00:07:13.870 --> 00:07:22.751
I was driving by Tulsa, ORU, and I saw the glory.

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:29.289
I started crying again.

00:07:29.289 --> 00:07:53.199
I saw the glory over the Mabee Center, and I saw the glory of the Lord over there again, and those old wells of revival from Oral Roberts and the greats that walked this land before and have gone home to be with the Lord.

00:07:53.199 --> 00:07:59.219
He said, "I'm going to do it one more time, and I'm bringing forth a great revival again, son.

00:07:59.559 --> 00:08:18.799
" Those old wells that have been capped for protection because the season was over for that, he said, "I'm bringing forth those great wells again, and I'm going to use you and I'm going to use these people for great healings.

00:08:19.279 --> 00:08:23.540
Demonstrations and manifestations of my glory will be seen again.

00:08:23.910 --> 00:08:27.908
I'm going to touch this generation one more time.

00:08:27.908 --> 00:08:32.400
" I told you, he said, "There's one more call.

00:08:32.400 --> 00:08:32.880
One last call.

00:08:33.680 --> 00:08:38.560
" And I've asked him because people were arguing with me and saying, "Oh, there's no great revival.

00:08:38.560 --> 00:08:41.919
That's not in the Bible in the last days.

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:45.867
" Well, I was out there and I said, "Lord, what do you say to this?

00:08:45.867 --> 00:08:50.959
" And he said, "Brandon, who's in control of time?

00:08:51.741 --> 00:08:53.306
" He said, "I am.

00:08:53.306 --> 00:08:57.920
Were you there when I threw the stars into space?

00:08:57.920 --> 00:09:01.227
Were you there when I created the heavens and the earth?

00:09:02.649 --> 00:09:09.910
" He was referring to Job whenever he was talking to Job.

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:16.160
He said, "Brandon, my heart is the harvest.

00:09:16.160 --> 00:09:20.000
My heart is the harvest.

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:21.560
One last call, son.

00:09:21.560 --> 00:09:26.320
I'm calling in the sheep from the back of the fold.

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:27.280
One last call.

00:09:27.280 --> 00:09:32.320
I'm calling them forth to come home, giving them an opportunity.

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:38.720
" And in this, I'm going to uncap those great wells of revival.

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:44.560
