00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:32.959
He's going to use Branson, Missouri.

00:10:32.959 --> 00:10:34.280
He's going to use these places.

00:10:34.280 --> 00:10:41.600
And he told me, "Those that are hungry and thirsty after righteousness, they will be filled with my glory.

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:51.040
" He said, "I want you to go back and I want to speak to you about Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

00:10:52.709 --> 00:10:57.340
" This time, he said, "This is the beginning of the glory.

00:11:15.120 --> 00:11:21.130
This is the beginning of what you have waited for for so long.

00:11:31.000 --> 00:11:31.600
" He talked about a great harvest of souls coming from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:37.783
